snippet.title: Bestiario - First Look Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Bestiario is an exciting turn-based combat JRPG based on Spanish mythology and folklore, full of surprises. Inspired by Japanese classics and the Persona saga, it naturally combines dynamic turn-based combat with an exciting, mature adventure.

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4games #ps4
